---
// Brief Service Overview component
---

<section class="py-20 lg:py-24 bg-background-secondary relative">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <!-- Value Proposition -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6">
        Deliver Real Results,
        <span class="bg-gradient-primary bg-clip-text text-transparent">Not Just Features</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        While others promise features, we deliver measurable outcomes. Orion transforms your business operations into profit-generating machines through intelligent automation and data-driven optimization.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Core Services Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      
      <!-- Revenue Growth -->
      <div class="text-center group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Generate 40% More Revenue</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Our clients see average revenue increases of 40% within 6 months through optimized workflows and automated sales processes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Cost Reduction -->
      <div class="text-center group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-accent rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Cut Operating Costs by 60%</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Eliminate manual processes and reduce operational overhead with intelligent automation that works 24/7.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Time Savings -->
      <div class="text-center group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary-main rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Save 25+ Hours Per Week</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Free your team from repetitive tasks to focus on high-value activities that drive growth and innovation.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Key Differentiator -->
    <div class="bg-background-card/80 backdrop-blur-xl border border-border-primary rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 text-center">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">
          What Makes Orion Different?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Unlike generic automation tools, Orion is purpose-built for results. We don't just automate processes—we optimize them for maximum ROI, providing real-time insights and continuous improvement recommendations.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-8">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-secondary-main rounded-full"></div>
            <span class="text-text-secondary font-medium">ROI-Focused Approach</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-primary-main rounded-full"></div>
            <span class="text-text-secondary font-medium">Continuous Optimization</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-secondary-accent rounded-full"></div>
            <span class="text-text-secondary font-medium">Measurable Outcomes</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- Background Effects -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1/3 h-full bg-gradient-radial opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-1/4 h-1/2 bg-gradient-mesh opacity-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
</section> 